            "title": "中國軍方9名官員被罷免人大代表職務",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"582\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bgRYmJYjQyBEWAXNfUVHtg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4b89474d577615588f36887a438275bf\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 新華社周四引述全國人大常委會的一份公告報導，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:中國人民解放軍陸軍;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/中國人民解放軍陸軍\">中國人民解放軍陸軍</a>司令員李橋銘和信息支援部隊政委李偉以及其他七名軍方官員的人大代表職務被罷免。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報導，被罷免第十四屆全國人大代表職務的人員還包括：陸軍的丁來富；中央軍委的邊瑞峰、王東海，海軍的沈金龍、秦生祥，空軍的於忠福，以及火箭軍的楊光。報導未透露罷免的具體原因。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"582\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UzkMr5XKSwpLeE.Wgt4vwg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/d992f571400a6c1ec20cbe2d8b7d67ad\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Ousts Nine Military Lawmakers as Xi’s Defense Purge Widens</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w